longBusinessSummary: Tajiri Resources Corp., an exploration stage company, engages in acquisition and exploration of mineral properties. It holds 100% interest in the Reo Gold Project comprising 7 exploration licenses covering an area of 1,002 square kilometers located in Burkina Faso. The company holds interests in the Guyana gold project. The company is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
